In software industry, a design pattern is general repeatable solution to Commonly occurring problem in software design.

Types:
    Creational 
    Behavioural 
    Structural
----------------
FDP:
It creates object for you rather you intiating object directly
FDP is also known as virtual constructor(C++ doesnt supoort virtual constructor)

compile:  g++ -o factoryPattern  client.cpp Object.cpp ToyFactory.cpp 
run: ./factoryPattern